Thanks for downloading our radio app! We hope you enjoy listening to your favorites radios. If you have any comments or questions regarding our app, or this policy, you can send us an email at
fbenslim@gmail.com
Contents
Our app radios includes the most popular radio stations in only one application and for several countries.
In one click, enjoy your favorite radio wherever you are through your internet connection (3g or wi-fi).
Amongst the strengths of this application:
- The app runs in the background listening and allows you to do other activities whilst continuing to listen your favorite station
- Its interface ergonomics is both intuitive and easy to use. In one click, you can select or change your station.
- The continuous update of the stations list (without updating application) will ensure you a better quality and a greater reactivity to problem solving
Please notice that our app is not responsible for what could be said on those radios.
Privacy Policy
Your privacy is important to us and we provide this policy which explains our information practices and usage.
Our radios apps may collect information including device info and browsing activity for statistical and security reasons as well as for improving the user experience. For example, we read you phone status in order to pause playback when you make or receive a call.
Our apps may use device identifiers to personalize content and ads and to analyze our traffic. We may share such identifiers and other information from your device with our advertising and analytics partners. You can learn more at http://www.google.com/intl/en/policies/privacy/partners/
We reserve the right to change this policy at anytime. You should check this page occasionally to ensure you are happy with any changes.